queries.query: SELECT Trial, EventId, Model, Time, Type, sum(Value) as Value, GeographySid, Country, Area, Subarea            FROM (SELECT * FROM LEDGER WHERE Value <> 0)           GROUP BY Trial, EventId, Model, Time, Type, GeographySid, Country, Area, Subarea
